                    <span>This book is both fun & practical, a boon to a "confident beginner" like myself. The instructions are very clear & the examples are gorgeous. Once you try this method, you might not want to go back, especially for machine-quilting.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">One of the better books</div>
